    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="http://losangeles.craigslist.org/lac/sec/6046005100.html"></div>
        </div>
Centurion Security Services, Inc. is currently hiring for our Hollywood, East LA, San Pedro, and Boyle Heights sites:<br>
<br>
<br>
Hollywood:<br>
<br>
Monday-Thursday: 2030 - 0400<br>
 <br>
<br>
East LA:<br>
<br>
Tuesday: 1600-0200<br>
<br>
Wednesday: 1600-0200<br>
<br>
<br>
Boyle Heights: Full and part-time shifts available. Hiring armed and unarmed guards.<br>
<br>
<br>
In order to work the port site, you need a TWIC card. The available shifts we have for the TWIC San Pedro Site are:<br>
<br>
Saturday: 0600-1400<br>
<br>
Saturday: 1400-2200 <br>
<br>
Sunday: 0600-1400<br>
<br>
<br>
On-call position for the San Pedro site is also available.<br>
<br>
<br>
**Please apply by sending an e-mail with your name, contact phone number, resume, days/hours available to work, and area interested in working.<br>
<br>
<br>
*Paid Sick Days after 90 days of employment.<br>
<br>
ALL candidates must have the following:<br>
<br>
-Valid CA BSIS Guard Card (Valid Firearms Permit if working armed).<br>
-Valid CA ID/Driver's License.<br>
-Professional "white-collar" appearance for residential sites (please no earrings/jewelry, visible <br>
tattoos.<br>
-Residential Experience is preferred, but not required for the residential sites.<br>
-Bi-lingual English/Spanish is preferred, but not required.<br>
-Reliable Transportation.<br>
-Able to stand on feet, and patrol on foot for the length of the shift, if required for that shift.<br>
-Must be able to write detailed logs clearly.<br>
<br>
Visit our web-site for more information: www.centurionssi.com<br>
<br>
We are an equal-opportunity employer. Due to the large number of responses we may not be able to reply to all applicants.    </section>

<ul class="notices">
            <li>Principals only. Recruiters, please don't contact this job poster.</li>
            <li>do NOT contact us with unsolicited services or offers</li>
</ul>

